 tmux cheatsheet                          prefix: C-a
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 Sessions
   prefix+$        rename session
   prefix+s        list/switch sessions
   prefix+d        detach

 Windows
   prefix+c        new window (current path)
   prefix+,        rename window
   prefix+w        list/switch windows
   prefix+&        kill window
   M-C-h / M-C-l   previous / next window
   M-C-j / M-C-k   swap window left / right

 Panes
   prefix+|        split horizontal (current path)
   prefix+-        split vertical (current path)
   prefix+h/j/k/l  select pane
   prefix+H/J/K/L  resize pane (repeatable)
   prefix+z        zoom/unzoom pane
   prefix+x        kill pane

 Copy mode (vi)
   prefix+Enter    enter copy mode
   v               begin selection
   y               copy selection
   q               quit copy mode

 Misc
   prefix+r        reload config
   prefix+:        command prompt
   prefix+?        list all bindings
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 press any key to close
